%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rs%207%20Crore%20'CCTV%20Fraud'%20Case%20Against%20AAP's%20Satyendar%20Jain%2C%20Deja%20Vu%20For%20AAP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECorruption%20charges%20continue%20to%20pile%20up%20outside%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Faap%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAam%20Aadmi%20Party%3C%2Fa%3E%20leaders'%20doors%2C%20with%20ex-Delhi%20Health%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Fsatyendar-jain%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESatyender%20Jain%3C%2Fa%3E%20back%20in%20the%20dock%20-%20this%20time%20amid%20allegations%20of%20bribery%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20Rs%20571%20crore%20project%20to%20install%20CCTV%20cameras%20in%20the%20city.%20The%20case%20has%20been%20pending%20since%20May%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%20has%20been%20filed%20by%20the%20Delhi%20government's%20Anti-Corruption%20Bureau%20-%20under%20Section%2017%20of%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Corruption%20Act%20-%20according%20to%20a%20statement%20released%20Wednesday%20afternoon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpecifically%2C%20Mr%20Jain%20is%20accused%20of%20taking%20Rs%207%20crore%20as%20a%20bribe%20to%20waive%20a%20Rs%2016%20crore%20penalty%20for%20delay%20in%20setting%20up%20cameras.%20Over%20one%20lakh%20CCTVs%20were%20to%20be%20set%20up%20across%20Delhi's%2070%20Assembly%20segments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ACB's%20case%20is%20built%20on%20the%20statement%20of%20%26quot%3Ban%20officer%20of%20the%20BEL%2C%20(who%20is)%20well-versed%20with%20the%20facts%20of%20the%20case%20(and)%20whose%20examination%20supported%20these%20allegations%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20officer%2C%20the%20ACB%20said%2C%20had%20provided%20a%20%26quot%3Bdetailed%20complaint%26quot%3B%2C%20which%20includes%20claims%20a%20second%20order%2C%20of%20an%20additional%201.4%20lakh%20cameras%2C%20was%20placed%20after%20the%20initial%20delay%20and%20of%20%26quot%3Bshoddy%26quot%3B%20installations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party's%20Delhi%20unit%20chief%2C%20Virendra%20Sachdeva%2C%20has%20ripped%20into%20the%20AAP%20over%20these%20latest%20claims%20and%20accused%20the%20party%20of%20trying%20to%20%26quot%3Bstifle%20the%20case%26quot%3B%20while%20it%20was%20in%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTender%20of%20Rs%20571%20crore%20was%20given%20to%20Bharat%20Electronics%20Limited%20and%20then%2C%20to%20waive%20off%20losses%2C%20he%20(Mr%20Jain)%20took%20Rs%207%20crore%20bribe.%20BJP%20had%20complained%20then%20also...%20the%20AAP%20tried%20to%20suppress%20investigation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged%2C%20%26quot%3B...%20but%20no%20matter%20how%20much%20you%20tried%20to%20hide%20the%20corruption%2C%20you%20have%20to%20answer%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeither%20the%20AAP%20nor%20Mr%20Jain%20have%20yet%20responded%20to%20these%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fresh%20case%20against%20Mr%20Jain%20-%20granted%20bail%20in%20October%20last%20year%2C%20following%20his%20arrest%20two%20years%20prior%20in%20an%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20money%20laundering%20case%20-%20is%20not%20the%20only%20bad%20news%3B%20last%20month%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20greenlit%20his%20prosecution%20in%20a%20disproportionate%20assets%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20and%20Mr%20Sisodia%20-%20both%20of%20whom%20were%20arrested%20and%20jailed%20on%20corruption%20charges%20linked%20to%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20excise%20policy%20scam%20-%20face%20new%20charges%20of%20their%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAAP%20boss%20and%20ex-Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20faces%20a%20six-year-old%20charge%20-%20misusing%20public%20funds%20to%20put%20up%20promotional%20posters%20for%20his%20party%2C%20and%20his%20former%20deputy%20is%20roiled%20in%20a%20Rs%202%2C000%20crore%20scam%20relating%20to%20the%20construction%20of%20classrooms%20for%20Delhi%20government%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20liquor%20policy%20charges%20also%20remain%3B%20last%20month%20the%20Comptroller%