C%20his%20parents-%20both%20daily-wage%20workers-%20filed%20a%20complaint%20with%20GRP%20on%20March%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20was%20caught%20on%20CCTV%2C%20which%20helped%20us%20track%20the%20accused%2C%26quot%3B%20SHO%20Arun%20Chaudhary%20of%20the%20GRP%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Police%20detained%20the%20young%20couple%20from%20Mahuwa%20in%20the%20Dausa%20district%20of%20Rajasthan%20two%20days%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20GRP%20eventually%20located%20the%20couple%20and%20returned%20the%20child%20to%20his%20parents%20within%2048%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20child%20was%20found%20safe%20and%20the%20accused%20were%20taken%20into%20custody%20when%20police%20arrived%20at%20their%20address%20on%20Sunday%20and%20searched%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAjmer%20GRP%20DSP%20Narender%20Singh%20noted%20that%20Jeevika%2C%20a%20mother%20of%20two%2C%20had%20been%20living%20with%20Kashyap%2C%20a%20worker%20who%20earned%20a%20daily%20wage%2C%20since%20leaving%20her%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20unable%20to%20conceive%20due%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bsterilisation%20procedure.%26quot%3B%20Singh%20added%20that%20the%20couple%20%26quot%3Btried%20medical%20options%20to%20have%20a%20child%20but%20failed%2C%20and%20they%20plotted%20to%20kidnap%20a%20child%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Times%20of%20India%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20couple%20had%20been%20preparing%20to%20kidnap%20a%20child%20for%20almost%20eight%20months%20and%20had%20spent%20hours%20conducting%20research%20at%20the%20train%20station%20before%20carrying%20out%20their%20plot%2C%20the%20investigation%20revealed.%20The%20couple%20reportedly%20packed%20clothes%2C%20snacks%2C%20and%20milk%20in%20a%20bag%20when%20they%20travelled%20to%20the%20train%20station%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20kidnapping.%20They%20took%20a%20bus%20to%20Mahuwa%20after%20kidnapping%20the%20youngster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKashyap%20and%20Jeevika%20intended%20to%20name%20the%20boy%20and%20even%20considered%20calling%20him%20Ashish%2C%20police%20said.%20%26quot%3BJeevika%20insisted%20the%20boy%20call%20her%20'mummy'.%20The%20accused%20couple%20was%20arrested%20under%20BNS%20Section%20137(2)%20for%20kidnapping%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20DSP%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742377620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Frdgie00g_rajasthan_625x300_19_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Funable-to-conceive-rajasthan-couple-kidnaps-child-from-jaipur-railway-station-7957829%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20couple%20reportedly%20packed%20clothes%2C%20snacks%2C%20and%20milk%20in%20a%20bag%20when%20they%20travelled%20to%20the%20train%20station%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20kidnapping.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Before%20Sunita%20Williams'%20Splashdown%2C%20Moments%20Of%20Terror%20In%20Spacecraft%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20Dragon%20spacecraft%20bringing%20astronauts%20Sunita%20Williams%20and%20Butch%20Wilmore%20home%20after%20nine%20months%20in%20space%20splashed%20down%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Florida%20at%205.57%20pm%20(3.27%20am%20IST).%20Shortly%20after%2C%2059-year-old%20Williams%20and%2062-year-old%20Wilmore%20were%20brought%20out%20of%20the%20spacecraft%2C%20smiling%20and%20waving%2C%20as%20the%20world%20cheered.%20NASA's%20Nick%20Hague%2C%20and%20Roscosmos%20cosmonaut%20Aleksandr%20Gorbunov%20accompanied%20them%20on%20the%2017-hour%20journey%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20these%20moments%20of%20joy%20were%20preceded%20by%20hours%20during%20which%20the%20astronauts%20--%20and%20the%20world%20--%20had%20their%20fingers%20crossed.%20And%20the%20last%20leg%20was%20the%20most%20tricky%20when%20SpaceX's%20Dragon%20spacecraft%20re-entered%20the%20atmosphere.%20At%20this%20point%2C%20the%20capsule%20is%20travelling%20at%20speeds%20going%20up%20to%2028%2C800%20kmph.%20The%20friction%20this%20creates%20takes%20the%20temperatures%20of%20its%20outer%20casing%20to%20about%201%2C600%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20with%20heat%20shields%20protecting%20the%20occupants%20inside.%20So%2C%20the%20cheers%20to%20celebrate%20Sunita%20Williams'%20homecoming%20came%20only%20after%20the%20spacecraft%20turned%20a%20ball%20of%20fire%20entering%20the%20atmosphere%20and%20heading%20for%20a%20splash%20in%20the%20ocean.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Protects%20The%20Astronauts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDocked%20at%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%2C%20the%20Dragon%20spacecraft%20is%20in%20a%20state%20of%20near-vacuum.%20Following%20a%20series%20of%20departure%20burns%2C%20it%20moved%20away%20from%20the%20station%20and%20began%20its%20journey%20home.%20As%20it%20enters%20Earth's%20atmosphere%2C%20high%20friction%20is%20created%2C%20pushing%20the%20temperatures%20up%20significantly%2C%20as%20high%20as%201%2C600%20degrees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Dragon%20capsules%20use%20heat-resistant%20PICA%20material%20for%20the%20outer%20shell.%20Photo%20courtesy%3A%20NASA%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Dragon%20capsules%20use%20heat-resistant%20PICA%20material%20for%20the%20outer%20shell.%20Photo%20courtesy%3A%20NASA%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fempi7nag_nasa-pica_625x300_19_March_25.jpg%3Fim%3DFitAndFill%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDragon%20capsules%20use%20heat-resistant%20PICA%20material%20for%20the%20outer%20shell.%20Photo%20courtesy%3A%20NASA%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SpaceX's%20Dragon%20capsule%20is%20equipped%20with%20a%20heat-resistant%20casing%20of%20Phenolic-Impregnated%20Carbon%20Ablator%20of%20PICA.%20It%20was%20NASA%20that%20first%20used%20this%20lightweight%20material.%20Later%2C%20SpaceX%20got%20its%20Dragon%20capsule%20outfitted%20with%20PICA%20tiles%20for%20cargo%20and%20human%20movement%20to%20and%20from%20the%20