%20guard%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they're%20not%20paying%20much%20attention%20to%20the%20company's%20recent%20rise%20to%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20says%20Justin%20Fung%2C%20a%20senior%20engineer%20at%20the%20company%2C%20who%20doesn't%20believe%20external%20interest%20is%20having%20much%20of%20an%20effect%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-culture-best-for-self-starters-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENvidia's%20culture%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20don't%20really%20talk%20about%20how%20much%20their%20equity%20is%20worth%2C%20because%20they%20were%20never%20really%20there%20for%20the%20equity%2C%26quot%3B%20Fung%20said%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DFsKLn1nQWVY%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20%26quot%3BCodesmith%26quot%3B%20podcast.%20%26quot%3BThey%20really%20just%20liked%20what%20they%20were%20doing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20has%20gained%20fame%20as%20one%20of%20the%20leading%20companies%20driving%20the%20AI%20boom%2C%20but%20before%20that%2C%20despite%20enjoying%20relatively%20consistent%20success%20in%20the%20GPU%20space%2C%20it%20wasn't%20a%20household%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20really%20interesting%20company%20because%20it%20only%20became%20famous%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Fung%20said.%20The%20initial%20broader%20spark%20of%20interest%20from%20the%20outside%20world%2C%20he%20added%2C%20came%20thanks%20to%20the%20gold%20rush%20on%20crypto.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20realized%20that%20you%20could%20mine%20Bitcoin%20using%20these%20computers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20that%20was%20the%20first%20step%20into%20the%20public%20consciousness%20%E2%80%94%20and%20then%20the%20next%20big%20one%20was%20obviously%20AI.%20People%20figured%20out%20that%20you%20could%20run%20these%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mit.edu%2F2017%2Fexplained-neural-networks-deep-learning-0414%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eneural%20networks%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20these%20GPUs%2C%20and%20that%20sent%20it%20to%20the%20stratosphere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20its%20explosion%20in%20popularity%20has%20come%20a%20corresponding%20spike%20in%20employee%20compensation%20%E2%80%94%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-jesen-huang-company-workforce-growth-stock-price-climbing-2024-11%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIt%2527s%2520one%2520of%2520the%2520best%252Dpaying%2520firms%2520in%2520Silicon%2520Valley.%26amp%3Btext%3DAs%2520of%2520January%25202024%252C%2520Nvidia%2527s%2Ctech%2520giants%2520in%2520the%2520dust.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENvidia's%20median%20salary%3C%2Fa%3E%20surpassing%20%24220%2C000%20as%20of%202024.%20For%20Fung%2C%20having%20a%20role%20at%20Nvidia%20represented%20a%20turnaround%20in%20his%20finances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody%20knows%20the%20equity%2C%20the%20stock%20has%20risen%20exponentially%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Fung%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20in%20a%20very%20comfortable%20place%20compared%20to%20where%20I%20used%20to%20be.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFung%20said%20Nvidia%20doesn't%20have%20high%20turnover%2C%20so%20many%20of%20his%20coworkers%20are%20holdovers%20from%20when%20the%20company%20was%20primarily%20associated%20with%20the%20gaming%20industry.%20They're%20lifers%20who%20joined%20%E2%80%94%20and%20stayed%20%E2%80%94%20largely%20thanks%20to%20their%20passion%20for%20the%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20have%20been%20working%20there%20before%20this%20company%20was%20famous%2C%20and%20they'd%20make%20gaming%20rigs%2C%26quot%3B%20Fung%20said.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20that%20come%20from%20that%20era%20are%20very%20humble%2C%20just%20from%20a%20previous%20generation%20of%20technology.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20unless%20it's%20intern%20season%2C%20Fung%20said%20younger%20employees%20are%20a%20relatively%20rare%20sight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody's%20super%20nice%20and%20I%20love%20all%20my%20co-workers%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20think%20the%20turnover%20is%20as%20high%2C%20so%20you%20don't%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20younger%20millennials%20or%20Gen%20Z%20people%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20many%20of%20its%20peers%20in%20the%20tech%20field%2C%20Fung%20said%20Nvidia%20never%20really%20developed%20a%20%26quot%3Bstartup%26quot%3B%20culture.%20Instead%2C%20he%20added%2C%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang's%20vision%20for%20the%20company%20has%20remained%20relatively%20consistent%20since%20its%20inception.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNvidia%2C%20despite%20being%20as%20popular%20as%20it%20was%2C%20never%20really%20had%20the%20culture%20of%20being%20a%20startup%20%E2%80%94%20say%20Airbnb%20or%20Snapchat%20%E2%80%94%20where%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20young%20people%20having%20fun%20and%20doing%20work%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Fung%20said.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20unlike%20other%20big%20names%20in%20tech%20like%20Google%20or%20Facebook%2C%20Nvidia%20isn't%20in%20the%20business%20of%20hiring%20%26quot%3Bgeneralists%26quot%3B%20and%20plugging%20them%20in%20wherever%20they%20fit%2C%20Fung%20said.%20Instead%2C%20they're%20often%20looking%20for%20people%20with%20hyper-specific%20skillsets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20really%20only%20got%20the%20position%20though%2C%20because%20my%20alignment%2C%20my%20background%2C%20was%20like%20perfectly%20aligned%20with%20the%20role%2C%26quot%3B%20Fung%20said.%20And%20I%20have%20seen%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20apply%20to%20Nvidia%20who%20were%20not%20as%20lucky.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20by%20Business%20Insider%20prior%20to%20publication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-engineer-why-staff-dont-talk-about-