sider.com%2Faapl-stock-price-warren-buffett-bull-case-for-apple-2018-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBuffett%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuffett%20likes%20Apple%20for%20similar%20reasons%20he%20loves%20utilities%20and%20other%20vaguely%20boring%2C%20profitable%20companies.%20Many%20people%20need%20what%20these%20companies%20sell%2C%20which%20helps%20them%20generate%20large%2C%20reliable%20returns%20%E2%80%94%20including%20juicy%20dividends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d3022ccd-3322-4fe8-bc88-a0287e35593c%5C%22%3E'Panic'%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Silicon%20Valley%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225205%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20panicked%20human%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d9cda5b8b41a9673fb03c8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223904%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20panicked%20human.%20Where's%20his%20iPhone%3F%3Cp%3Eizusek%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EElectricity.%20Water.%20An%20iPhone.%20These%20are%20essential%20ingredients%20for%20modern%20life.%20Without%20them%2C%20things%20can%20get%20difficult%20quickly.%20Take%20my%20family's%20experience%20as%20an%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20wife's%20iPhone%20was%20stolen%20last%20year.%20She%20only%20waited%20a%20few%20hours%20before%20driving%20to%20the%20nearest%20Apple%20store%20to%20hand%20over%20almost%20%241%2C000%20for%20a%20replacement.%20She%20described%20the%20thought%20of%20existing%20without%20an%20iPhone%20as%20%26quot%3Bpanic.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%20up%3A%20She%20used%20two-factor%20authentication%20via%20her%20iPhone%20to%20access%20sensitive%20work%20documents.%20She%20couldn't%20work%20without%20a%20new%20Apple%20device.%20(She's%20added%20a%20backup%20now.%20Guess%20what%20it%20is%3F%20An%20iPad!)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20a%20long%20list%20of%20other%20practical%20tasks%20revealed%20themselves%20to%20be%20difficult%20without%20an%20iPhone%3A%20Booking%20an%20exercise%20class%2C%20texting%20a%20group%20of%20friends%2C%20keeping%20streaks%20going%20on%20mobile%20games%2C%20and%20accessing%20the%20iPhone's%20digital%20wallet%20for%20tickets%20she%20needed%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20daughter%20broke%20her%20iPhone%20beyond%20repair%20last%20year.%20She%20experienced%20similar%20panic%20and%20bought%20a%20replacement%20from%20Apple%20within%2024%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20uses%20a%20mobile%20app%20on%20her%20iPhone%20to%20authenticate%20and%20access%20her%20college%20accounts%20for%20submitting%20homework%20and%20doing%20other%20study-related%20stuff.%20She%20also%20had%20a%20plane%20to%20catch%20and%20was%20worried%20about%20not%20having%20the%20digital%20ticket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20wife%20and%20daughter%20both%20worried%20about%20the%20data%20on%20their%20iPhones%20and%20thought%20it%20would%20be%20safer%20and%20easier%20to%20get%20a%20new%20iPhone%20to%20reclaim%20this%20digital%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20my%20iPhone%20SE's%20battery%20started%20running%20low%2C%20and%20I%20struggled%20to%20hear%20people%20well%20on%20phone%20calls.%20These%20problems%20were%20fixable%20and%20probably%20related%20to%20user%20error.%20I%20could%20have%20gotten%20a%20new%20battery%20from%20Apple%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20yet%20I%20just%20could%20not%20be%20bothered.%20So%20I%20bought%20a%20new%20iPhone%2016e.%20It%20was%20so%20easy%2C%20and%20my%20life%20was%20uninterrupted.%20I%20did%20not%20think%20about%20AI%20once%20during%20this%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228f0b6c7e-b495-433e-a7bf-bda82423fe6a%5C%22%3EAndroid%20switching%20doesn't%20really%20happen%20anymore%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20wife%2C%20my%20daughter%2C%20and%20I%20did%20not%20ever%20once%20consider%20getting%20an%20Android%20phone%20instead.%20For%20many%20non-technical%20consumers%2C%20switching%20is%20too%20complex.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20wife%20knew%20her%20stolen%20iPhone%20was%20backed%20up%20in%20Apple's%20iCloud%2C%20so%20getting%20the%20same%20device%20again%20made%20the%20replacement%20process%20much%20quicker%20and%20smoother.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20knew%20that%20if%20I%20bought%20another%20one%2C%20it%20would%20be%20as%20painless%20as%20possible%20to%20access%20my%20photos%2C%20wallet%2C%20apps%2C%20contacts%2C%20etc%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20me.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20already%20pained%20by%20the%20stolen%20iPhone.%20Switching%20to%20Android%20at%20that%20moment%20made%20no%20sense.%20I'd%20have%20been%20breaking%20myself%20into%20jail.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%202023%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcirpapple.substack.com%2Fp%2Fapple-to-android-and-android-to-apple%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Consumer%20Intelligence%20Research%20Partners%20estimated%20that%20only%20about%204%25%20of%20Android%20phone%20buyers%20switched%20from%20an%20iPhone.%20The%20authors%20wrote%20that%20a%20big%20reason%20was%20%26quot%3Bfear%20of%20the%20complexity%20of%20switching.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20not%20a%20lot%20of%20iOS-to-Android%20switching%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Josh%20Lowitz%2C%20a%20partner%20at%20CIRP.%20%26quot%3BSwitching%20between%20platforms%20is%20not%20that%20difficult%2C%20but%20the%20habits%20and%20iOS-specific%20apps%20and%20connections%20are%20hard%20to%20leave.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20why%20a%20year%20or%20so%20of%20delay%20in%20AI%20features%20won't%20matter%20much.%20When%20everyone's%20iPhone%20stops%20working%2C%20they%20will%20buy%20another%2C%20with%20or%20without%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20we%20should%20watch%3A%20How%20many%20old%20iPhones%20will%20Apple%20stop%20supporting%3F%20The%20company%20does%20an%20amazing%20job%20keeping%20these%20devices%20running%20for%20years.%20But%20after%20a%20certain%20point%2C%20the%20hardware%20just%20can't%20keep%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20when%20some%20handsets%20are%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fiphone-compatible-ios-18-ap