20of%20this%20month.%20In%20December%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ceo-company-cut-manager-vp-roles-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECEO%20Sundar%20Pichai%3C%2Fa%3E%20told%20staff%20that%20Google%20had%20cut%20vice%20president%20and%20manager%20roles%20by%2010%25%20as%20part%20of%20its%20efficiency%20drive.%20Microsoft%20also%20monitors%20what%20it%20calls%20%26quot%3Bspan%20of%20control%2C%26quot%3B%20tracking%20the%20number%20of%20reports%20per%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c48f3a74-fb79-44da-ad74-c9f848db379d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPerformance%20pressures%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20cuts%2C%20employees%20across%20the%20industry%20say%20companies%20are%20dialing%20up%20the%20performance%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-job-cuts-everything-we-know-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMeta%20told%20staff%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20January%20that%20it%20would%20eliminate%20roughly%205%25%20of%20its%20workforce%2C%20or%20about%204%2C000%20employees%2C%20to%20%26quot%3Braise%20the%20bar%20on%20performance%20management%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20Zuckerberg%20wrote%20in%20an%20internal%20memo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGoogle%20also%20increased%20pressure%20on%20employees.%20Perhaps%20most%20telling%20was%20Pichai's%20December%20comments%20attempting%20to%20clarify%20what%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ceo-googleyness-sundar-pichai-2024-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGoogleyness%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20means%20for%20a%20modern%20Google.%20Once%20a%20squishy%20and%20vague%20philosophy%20for%20the%20search%20giant's%20corporate%20culture%2C%20Pichai%20said%20he%20believed%20it%20now%20meant%2C%20among%20other%20things%2C%20being%20%26quot%3Bmission%20first.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20more%20pressure%20for%20individuals%20to%20be%20better%20in%20their%20roles%2C%20and