0asked%20me%20back%20then%20what%20I%20thought%20would%20take%20the%20market%20down%2C%20I'm%20certain%20my%20answer%20was%20that%2C%20if%20we%20knew%20then%20it's%20already%20priced%20in%2C%26quot%3B%20Meisler%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20the%20answer%20is%2C%20I%20never%20know.%20It's%20always%20going%20to%20be%20something%20from%20left%20field.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelow%20are%20five%20charts%20Meisler%20is%20focusing%20on%20this%20week%20to%20gauge%20market%20sentiment%20and%20the%20stock%20market's%20near-term%20outlook.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22151d1f5a-c673-4e4c-8364-06736bae03fa%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMarket%20charts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chart%20below%20shows%20the%20number%20of%20stocks%20making%20new%2052-week%20lows%20traded%20on%20the%20Nasdaq%20Composite%20Index.%20It%20shows%20that%20over%20the%20past%20week%2C%20fewer%20stocks%20have%20made%20new%20lows%2C%20indicating%20that%20selling%20is%20drying%20up%20and%20bearish%20sentiment%20is%20slowing%20down.%20Meisler%20focused%20on%20the%20Nasdaq%20this%20week%20since%20the%20index%20saw%20the%20steepest%20pullback%20of%20the%20three%20major%20indexes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nasdaq%20Composite%20New%20Lows%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d9c335b8b41a9673fb018c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22312%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EStockCharts.%20com%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chart%20below%20shows%20overall%20market%20breadth%2C%20which%20tracks%20most%20stocks.%20It%20recently%20made%20a%20higher%20low%2C%20suggesting%20that%20selling%20pressure%20is%20subsiding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20the%20lower%20chart%20for%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20shows%20the%20index%20continued%20to%20make%20a%20lower%20low%2C%20indicating%20a%20divergence%20as%20investors%20continued%20to%20shed%20off%20riskier%2C%20rich%20technology%20stocks.%20Still%2C%20it's%20a%20good%20sign%20because%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20stocks%20had%20been%20the%20mover%20of%20the%20major%20index.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20it%20tells%20you%20that%20the%20index%20movers%20are%20pulling%20the%20index%20down%2C%20but%20for%20the%20majority%20of%20stocks%2C%20the%20selling%20has%20stopped%2C%26quot%3B%20Meisler%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22NYSE%20Breadth%20(top)%20and%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20(bottom)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d9c42269253ccddf999b38%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22421%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EHelene%20Meisler%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBelow%20is%20a%20chart%20that%20shows%20stocks%20trading%20on%20the%20NYSE%20were%20in%20overbought%20territory%20in%20the%20final%20quarter%20of%202024.%20As%20we%20neared%202025%2C%20overbought%20peaks%20were%20making%20lower%20highs%2C%20indicating%20that%20buying%20pressure%20was%20drying%20up.%20However%2C%20March's%20oversold%20trough%20remained%20higher%20than%20December's%20oversold%20trough%2C%20suggesting%20there's%20now%20less%20momentum%20on%20the%20downside%2C%20Meisler%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20stocks%20remain%20in%20oversold%20territory%2C%20they%20are%20beginning%20to%20recover%20as%20the%20oscillator%20approaches%20the%20zero%20or%20neutral%20mark.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chart%20below%20is%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2FStockCharts.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStockCharts.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22NYSE%20overbought%2Foversold%20Oscillator%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d9c45fb8b41a9673fb01dc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22312%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EStockCharts.com%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESince%202024%2C%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500's%20highs%20were%20accompanied%20by%20bulls%20at%2060%25%20based%20on%20data%20from%20the%20Investors%20Intelligence%20Survey%2C%20a%20sentiment%20survey%20for%20attitudes%20of%20US%20advisors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%2060%25%20is%20typically%20too%20many%20bulls%2C%20Meisler%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20can't%20think%20of%20in%20my%20career%2C%20and%20I've%20been%20doing%20this%20since%201982%2C%20I%20can't%20think%20of%20one%20time%20we%20went%20over%2070%25.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EData%20from%20the%20previous%20week%20shows%20the%20bears%20are%20only%20at%2027%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22839%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bullish%20sentiment%20versus%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d9c48e585f1dff88b27fbf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22423%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EData%20investors%20Intelligence%2C%20chart%20by%20Meisler.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20up%20to%20investors%20to%20decide%20what%20side%20of%20the%20market%20they'd%20rather%20be%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20an%20old%20trader%20friend%20who%20always%20says%2C%20sometimes%20you%20want%20to%20be%20on%20the%20outside%20looking%20in%2C%20rather%20than%20on%20the%20inside%20wishing%20you%20were%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Meisler%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20to%20me%20the%20market%20has%20that%20feeling%20to%20it%20right%20now.%20But%20if%20we%20got%20panic%2C%20I'd%20be%20bullish.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-correction-charts-what-happens-next-outlook-helene-meisler-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742373002000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F670937866ac7b701e7ca63b6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-correction-charts-what-happens-next-outlook-helene-meisler-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Helene%20Me