oklyn%20in%201915%2C%20Underhill%20was%20a%20Harvard%20graduate%20who%20entered%20the%20intelligence%20world%20during%20World%20War%20II.%20His%20work%20in%20the%20Military%20Intelligence%20Service%20(MIS)%20earned%20him%20a%20War%20Department%20staff%20citation%20for%20excellence.%20Post-war%2C%20he%20was%20eyed%20for%20CIA%20recruitment%2C%20though%20records%20indicate%20he%20was%20to%20be%20approached%20cautiously%20and%20granted%20only%20limited%20access%20to%20classified%20material.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20mid-1950s%2C%20Underhill%20was%20a%20well-connected%20journalist%20and%20consultant%2C%20writing%20for%20Life%20and%20Esquire%2C%20often%20critical%20of%20US%20military%20preparedness.%20His%20interactions%20with%20intelligence%20agencies%20continued%2C%20particularly%20in%20relation%20to%20Soviet%20military%20analysis.%20He%20had%20once%20informed%20the%20FBI%20and%20CIA%20about%20Herman%20Axelbank%2C%20a%20man%20peddling%20photographs%20of%20Soviet%20military%20assets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECIA%20and%20FBI%20Connections%20to%20Oswald%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20newly%20released%20documents%20add%20to%20existing%20doubts%20about%20Lee%20Harvey%20Oswald's%20role.%20While%20the%20official%20record%20states%20that%20Oswald%20acted%20alone%2C%20inconsistencies%20remain.%20The%20timing%20of%20the%20shots%2C%20bullet%20trajectory%2C%20and%20witness%20testimonies%20suggest%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20second%20shooter.%20The%20Zapruder%20film%20-%20which%20shows%20President%20Kennedy%20and%20his%20motorcade%20in%20Dealey%20Plaza%20in%20downtown%20Dallas%20-%20captures%20the%20assassination%2C%20and%20shows%20Kennedy's%20head%20moving%20backwards%2C%20contradicting%20the%20idea%20that%20all%20shots%20came%20from%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22John%20F%20Kennedy%2C%20his%20wife%20Jacqueline%2C%20Texas%20governor%20John%20Connally%2C%20and%20Connallys%20wife%20Nellie%20in%20the%2