uting%20foreign%20arms.%20Documents%20indicate%20that%20he%20worked%20closely%20with%20intelligence%20agencies%20in%20the%20US%20and%20abroad%2C%20including%20West%20German%20intelligence%20(BND)%2C%20and%20may%20have%20played%20a%20role%20in%20clandestine%20arms%20deals%20related%20to%20anti-Castro%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20company%2C%20International%20Armament%20Corporation%20(Interarmco)%2C%20was%20involved%20in%20supplying%20weapons%20to%20resistance%20groups.%20While%20there%20is%20no%20direct%20link%20between%20Cummings%20and%20the%20JFK%20assassination%2C%20his%20activities%20and%20ties%20to%20intelligence%20agencies%20have%20raised%20questions%20about%20the%20events%20leading%20up%20to%20November%2022%2C%201963.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20enduring%20mystery%20is%20why%20Jack%20Ruby%20-%20a%20Dallas%20nightclub%20owner%20with%20reported%20ties%20to%20organised%20crime%20-%20shot%20Oswald%20two%20days%20after%20the%20assassination.%20While%20Ruby%20claimed%20he%20was%20acting%20out%20of%20grief%20for%20Kennedy%2C%20sceptics%20argue%20he%20was%20silencing%20Oswald%20before%20he%20could%20reveal%20more%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERuby's%20trial%20and%20his%20subsequent%20death%20from%20cancer%20while%20in%20custody%20have%20only%20deepened%20suspicions.%20Adding%20to%20the%20intrigue%2C%20one%20of%20the%20doctors%20who%20treated%20him%20in%20prison%2C%20Louis%20Jolyon%20West%2C%20was%20involved%20in%20MKULTRA%2C%20the%20CIA's%20mind-control%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKey%20pieces%20of%20physical%20evidence%20in%20the%20JFK%20case%20remain%20controversial.%20The%20%26quot%3Bmagic%20bullet%26quot%3B%20theory%2C%20which%20suggests%20a%20single%20bullet%20hit%20both%20Kennedy%20and%20Texas%20Governor%20John%20Connally%2C%20has%20been%20widely%20criticized%20for%20its%20implausibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742368860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fbn9312go_john-f-kennedy-ndtv-_625x300_19_March_25