20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnergy%20storage%20has%20been%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpower-grid-strain-home-vehicle-electrification-ai-startups-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekey%20bottleneck%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20renewables%20industry.%20Because%20wind%20and%20solar%20power%20are%20intermittent%2C%20it's%20hard%20to%20forecast%20how%20much%20electricity%20these%20sources%20can%20produce.%20Excess%20energy%20can%20go%20to%20waste%20if%20there%20isn't%20enough%20demand%20for%20it%20at%20the%20time%20of%20generation.%20One%20way%20that%20energy%20storage%20providers%20prevent%20that%20is%20by%20using%20batteries%20so%20energy%20can%20be%20saved%20and%20deployed%20when%20there's%20more%20demand%20from%20the%20grid.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECapalo%20AI's%20model%20takes%20in%20multiple%20data%20points%2C%20from%20weather%20forecasting%20to%20consumers'%20energy%20consumption%20levels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20model%20then%20decides%2C%20how%20do%20we%20run%20and%20schedule%20this%20battery%20charging%20so%20we%20can%20provide%20the%20right%20commitments%20to%20the%20grid%3F%26quot%3B%20Taskinen%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup's%20virtual%20power%20plants%20then%20send%20those%20data-driven%20commands%20to%20battery%20providers%2C%20instructing%20them%20when%20to%20charge%20and%20discharge%20based%20on%20the%20amount%20of%20energy%20being%20generated%2C%20grid%20capacity%2C%20and%20consumer%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThen%20we%20decide%20how%20to%20utilize%20these%20batteries%2C%20so%20the%20battery%20owner%20can%20maximize%20how%20much%20they%20earn%2C%20and%20the%20grid%20benefits%20as%20much%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20Taskinen%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20then%20makes%20energy%20bids%20to%20the%20electricity%20markets.%20%26quot%3BWe%20agree%20on%20the%20commitments%20to%20provide%20energy%20output%20to%20the%20grid%2C%20which%20we%20then%20dispatch%20from%20the%20batteries