ew-9%20astronauts%20as%20they%20returned%20to%20Earth%20after%20over%20nine%20months%20of%20stay%20in%20space.%20%26quot%3BWelcome%20back%2C%20%23Crew9!%20The%20Earth%20missed%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20wrote%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20along%20with%20a%20picture%20with%20Ms%20Williams.%20NASA's%20Crew-9%20returned%20early%20Wednesday%20morning%2C%20in%20SpaceX's%20Dragon%20spacecraft%20and%20splashed%20down%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Florida%20at%203%3A27%20am%20(IST).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EWelcome%20back%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FCrew9%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Crew9%3C%2Fa%3E!%20The%20Earth%20missed%20you.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnTheirs%20has%20been%20a%20test%20of%20grit%2C%20courage%20and%20the%20boundless%20human%20spirit.%20Sunita%20Williams%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FCrew9%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23Crew9%3C%2Fa%3E%20astronauts%20have%20once%20again%20shown%20us%20what%20perseverance%20truly%20means.%20Their%20unwavering%20determination%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20vast%20unknown%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FFkgagekJ7C%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FFkgagekJ7C%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Narendra%20Modi%20(%40narendramodi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnarendramodi%2Fstatus%2F1902235311071023195%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2019%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENASA%20astronauts%20Sunita%20Williams%20and%20Butch%20Wilmore%20flew%20aboard%20NASA's%20Boeing%20Crew%20Flight%20Test%20to%20space%20on%20June%205%20last%20year.%20The%20eight-day%20mission%20turned%20into%20a%20286-day%20stay%20as%20issues%20were%20reported%20in%20the%20Starliner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20defined%20the%20nine-month%20stay%20at%20the%20International%20Space%20Station%20(ISS)%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Btest%C2%A0of%20grit%2C%20courage%20and%20the%20boundless%20human%20spirit.%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20lauded%20astronauts'%C2%A0perseverance%20and%20determination%20amid%20uncertainty.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSunita%20Williams%20and%20the%20%23Crew9%20astronauts%20have%20once%20again%20shown%20us%20what%20perseverance%20truly%20means.%20Their%20unwavering%20determination%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20vast%20unknown%20will%20forever%20inspire%20millions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20further%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bspace%20exploration%20is%20about%20pushing%20the%20limits%20of%20human%20potential%2C%20daring%20to%20dream%2C%20and%20having%20the%20courage%20to%20turn%20those%20dreams%20into%20reality.%20Sunita%20Williams%2C%20a%20trailblazer%20and%20an%20icon%2C%20has%20exemplified%20this%20spirit%20throughout%20her%20career.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPM%20Modi%20also%20appreciated%20the%20team%20that%20worked%20tirelessly%20to%20ensure%20astronauts'%20safe%20return.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20incredibly%20proud...They%20have%20demonstrated%20what%20happens%20when%20precision%20meets%20passion%20and%20technology%20meets%20tenacity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESunita%20Williams'%20Journey%20From%20Earth%20To%20Space%20And%20Back%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENASA%20astronauts%20Sunita%20Williams%20and%20Butch%20Wilmore%20flew%20aboard%20NASA's%20Boeing%20Crew%20Flight%20Test%20to%20space%20on%20June%205%20last%20year.%20The%20two%20astronauts%20went%20on%20an%20eight-day%20mission%20to%20the%20ISS%20but%2C%20on%20June%206%2C%20as%20Starliner%20approached%20the%20space%20station%2C%20NASA%20and%20Boeing%20identified%20helium%20leaks%20and%20experienced%20issues%20with%20the%20spacecraft%20reaction%20control%20thrusters.%20The%20Starliner%20was%20sent%20back%20to%20Earth%20without%20the%20crew.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20in%20August%2C%20it%20was%20decided%20to%20reassign%20the%20two%20astronauts%20to%20SpaceX's%20Crew-9%20mission.%20This%20meant%2C%20downsizing%20the%20Crew-9%20from%20four%20to%20two%20and%20dropping%20NASA%20astronauts%20Zena%20Cardman%20and%20Stephanie%20Wilson%2C%20previously%20announced%20as%20crewmates%2C%20to%20make%20space%20for%20Ms%20Williams%20and%20Mr%20Wilmore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENASA%20astronaut%20Nick%20Hague%2C%20and%20Roscosmos%20cosmonaut%20Aleksandr%20Gorbunov%20flew%20to%20the%20space%20station%20as%20commander%20and%20mission%20specialist%2C%20respectively%2C%20as%20part%20of%20a%20two-crew%20member%20flight%20aboard%20a%20SpaceX%20Dragon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20after%20over%20nine%20months%2C%20the%20Crew-9%20team%20returned%20to%20earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%2017-hour-long%20journey%2C%20the%20spacecraft%20deployed%20its%20parachute%20before%20a%20splashdown%20in%20the%20ocean%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Florida.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742363940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fttl2b7mo_pm-modi-sunita-williams-_625x300_19_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwelcome-back-the-earth-missed-you-pm-modi-on-sunita-williams-return-7957527%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20post%20welcoming%20Sunita%20Williams%20and%20Crew-9%2C%20PM%20Modi%20said%20that%20space%20exploration%20is%20about%20pushing%20the%20limits%20of%20human%20potential%2C%20daring%20to%20dream%2C%20and%20having%20the%20courage%20to%20turn%20those%20dreams%20into%20reality.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwelcome-back-the-earth-missed-you-pm-modi-on-sunita-williams-return-7957527%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98They%20have%20to%20get%20better%20first%E2%80%99%3A%20Donald%20Trump%20announces%20Sunita%20Williams%20and%20Butch%20Wilmore%20will%20visit%20White%